HEADWORD: Atterrate
<hw>At*ter*rate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[It.
<ets>atterrare</ets> (cf. LL. <ets>atterrare</ets> to cast to earth); L.
<ets>ad</ets> + <ets>terra</ets> earth, land.]</ety> <def>To fill up
with alluvial earth.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
